CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 12, 1956, pg. A21 reads: " Visitors...in Pittsburgh for the Urban League Guild's Bal Masque, Dr. Yvonne Jones, Springfield, Mass.; Mmes. Alta Douglass, N.Y.; Sydney Taylor Brown, ball chairman; Mollie Moon and Florence Dixon of New York. - Harris PHoto."
TitMainTitle: Dr. Yvonne Jones, Alta Douglass, Sydney Taylor Brown, Mollie Moon, and Florence Dixon, posed in William Penn Hotel for Urban League Guild Bal Masque
